    "Standardised outcome measures between studies are crucial for better comparability.",
    "Future studies should use measures such as diagnostic accuracy, patient satisfaction, engagement and usability ratings.",
    "Instruments such as the System Usability Scale (SUS) or the Technology Acceptance Model (TAM) could be used.",
